<plot>Eckhart, a half-hour animated series, celebrates the pioneering spirit, and the joys and challenges of growing up in beautiful, magical Prince Edward Island. The family series explores really big themes from a very small perspective - that of a small mouse named Eckhart, who is full of irrepressible wonderment about the mysteries of his world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?165156</url></doc>
